                            <comment id="12455929" author="bayard" created="Wed, 6 Dec 2006 09:08:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like beanutils, cli, dbutils, digester, fileupload, lang, logging and scxml all have references to NOTICE.txt (and presumably LICENSE.txt). If the parent is doing it, sounds like they all could go. Sound plausible?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
